name: Warrior Princesses
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi - commissions open!
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

Warrior Princesses

Many of you loved the Paladin armor and the Dark Knight armor LoRA.

I have now come forward to give you something in-between: Warrior Princesses.

I hope that with Warrior Princesses you will be able to get creative and get THE armor of your dreams for your princesses.

Certainly, these damsels know no distress, they are armed to the teeth and ready to go to war!

Download this LoRA and come meet your Warrior Princess!
